date.headline: Sh*t Politicians Say
date.text: In true political fashion, his character rattles off common jargon heard from people running for office.

date.headline: Sh*t Nobody Says
date.text: Have you ever heard someone say “can I burn a copy of your Nickelback CD?” or “my Bazooka gum still has flavor!” Nobody says that.

asset.caption: Directed and Edited by Matt Mayer, Produced by Seth Keim, Written by Eliot Glazer. Featuring Eliot and Ilana Glazer, who are siblings, not married.
